-------
 ABOUT 
-------

ldrviewer is a simple command line program for handling LDR files.  LDR files 
are a Visual DSP invention for running code on the Blackfin CPU.  Sometimes 
we need to handle these things in the world of Linux as it is the native 
executable format for the Blackfin CPU.


